creator: ONEPOINTFOUR SOFT
descriptionHtml:
It is a simple clicker game.

If you touch the monsters on the screen, you can hit the headshot kick!
Acquire various masks and reincarnate to earn reincarnation points!

Buy artifacts and fight enemies with more powerful attack power!

Buy and upgrade more powerful masks and artifacts to repel enemies with a stronger look!

[Game description and method]
-Attack by touching the enemy on the screen!
-Buy masks with the gold you earn!
-Each mask has a reincarnation point!
-When reincarnating, you can earn as much as the reincarnation points of your own mask.
-Purchased masks and acquired gold disappear when reborn.
-The jewels and reincarnation points you have do not disappear even after reincarnation.
-Let's launch a powerful attack on enemies by acquiring various artifact items!
descriptionShort: Win, upgrade your mask, acquire and strengthen relics, and capture monsters!
